<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.93.10039.figure29>
    dc:description "Figure 29. Clathurella dichroma Sturany, 1903, Locality 25 (Abu Ghusun, Egypt, Red Sea). A-D, F, H. Figured syntype, NHMW 37717: front (A-B), right side (C), back (D), microsculpture (F), protoconch (H). E. Original figure by Sturany (1903). G. Original label. Scale bars: A-D: 0.5 mm, F, H: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118677" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

